data.description: 3.625% assumable mortgage and possible owner financing 2nd mortgage! Two bedrooms, two full baths & living area that includes a gourmet kitchen w/ air fry and convection ovens as well as drawer base cabinets and full overlay, soft close custom cabinetry located on the main floor.  The first floor egresses are all level with no steps & connected via concrete walkways.  The second floor offers a secondary kitchen with french door fridge and dishwasher as well as a loft with covered deck access & 4 bedrooms as well as 3 full bathrooms. Interior walls of bedrooms and bathrooms are insulated for noise cancellation.  Above the garage, one room is finished & the 2nd 1/2 has wiring, insulation, walls & ceilings ready to expand- see property sketch.  Outdoor living space includes a Wahoo Floating dock with a 10' by 24' covered slip as well as a 14'x14' party pad; a paver patio, covered patio and covered deck. 121’ shoreline on Fishing Creek Lake. Resort style amenities. Agent is an owner.
